ygData.messageBody:
Hahaha.. that's hillarious.. I'd love to see someone get whipped and go flying. Though it probably wouldn't be too funny if it was me :) Strange that the ogre had a key for you, I've killed him a ton of times and I don't think any of us has ever gotten a key. Oh well.. perhaps next time.

Tandayen, Dark Elf Wizard

From: shypht <evanschu@...>
To: eq_wizards@onelist.com <eq_wizards@onelist.com>
Date: Monday, April 19, 1999 8:59 AM
Subject: [eq_wizards] Re: Anyone Know


I think tentical-terrors range in the 20+ area, not that sure. Last time I was in Najena I was lvl 12 or so, and having fun but it was hard, we managed to kill the oger guard that held the key tho, which I snagged and now hold onto. One thing to look out for on TT's is getting whiped backwards, they can actually lift you off the ground and toss you backwards, was rather wied watching a lvl 14 sk that was training them fly around =)
